# Tic Tac Toe
![Tic Tac Toe by Maruf Sarker](img/tic-tac-toe-preview.png)

## Simple Tic Tac Toe Game

This is a simple Tic Tac Toe Game.

There are two modes of the game.
- **Easy Mode**
- **Normal Mode**

##Easy Mode

Easy Mode is where your AI (computing device) put its marks Randomly without considering your moves.

Easy mode, as its name, is easier to Win, harder to lose!

##Normal Mode

Normal Mode is where your AI (computing device) put its marks considering your moves. AI tries to follow Minimax Algorithm.

Normal Mode is a bit harder than Easy Mode, and fairly harder to Win and, Easy to Draw and, Easier to Lose!
